<title>Hint</title>
<para id="fs-id1167794060098">Start with <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>θ</m:mi><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> then use <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</commentary>
